These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
4 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg, domino, billiard
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, bus, roller, tram
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, gardening, chess, reading
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, balloon-flower, aconite, orchid
 1. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 2. the person playing snooker is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 5. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
 6. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 7. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person playing domino##1
 8. the person who growsaconite is in an even position##4
 9. the person who growstulip is between the person who growsorchid and the person driving the tram##2
10. the person playing snooker is the person who growsorchid##1
11. the person driving the roller is the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Game          | domino  | snooker    | billiard    | mah-jongg   |
| Transport   | bus     | boat   | roller       | tram    |
| Hobby   | gardening | card-games | reading    | chess |
| Flower           | balloon-flower | orchid       | tulip | aconite     |

