.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
House: wooden, victorian, tower, art-deco
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda, iced-tea, cola
4 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, mah-jongg, monopoly
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, tram, car, taxi
 1. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
 2. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the tower house##1
 4. the victorian house is the person playing snooker##1
 5. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the wooden house##1
 6. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
 7. the art-deco house is on the right of the tower house##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left or far right##3
10. the tower house is in an odd position##4
11. the person playing mah-jongg is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| House          | wooden  | victorian    | tower     | art-deco       |
| Beverage         | iced-tea | cola | lemonade   | mirinda |
| Game   | mah-jongg | snooker   | scrabble   | monopoly    |
| Transport         | car | taxi  | subway | tram   |

