.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, lilac, emerald, azure
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, sudoku, video-games, fishing
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, apple, onion, avocado
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, ice-hockey, basketball, rowing
 1. the person who likes mauve is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
 2. the person eating apple is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 3. the person who likes mauve is on the left or right of the person who likes emerald##3
 4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 5. the person who likes lilac is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 6. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person eating avocado##1
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4
 9. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
10. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person who likes emerald##1
11. the person who likes mauve is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Color      | mauve | emerald   | azure    | lilac      |
| Hobby           | video-games | photography | sudoku | fishing     |
| Food   | apple      | avocado   | cauliflower   | onion |
| Sport           | rowing         | skateboarding       | basketball  | ice-hockey       |

