There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, american, nigerian, dutch
 1. the person traveling to boston is the person who likes grey##1
 2. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
 3. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
 4. the bongani-smoker is in an even position##4
 5. the person traveling to paris is the dutch##1
 6. the nigerian is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
 7. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the nigerian##1
 8. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3
 9. the nigerian is the bongani-smoker##1
10. the mexican is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
11. the person traveling to rome is the person who likes lilac##1
12. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| City   | venice       | rome   | boston   | paris   |
| Color       | emerald        | lilac | grey    | apricot       |
| Cigar      | oliveros | bongani    | swisher  | siglo |
| Nationality      | american  | nigerian  | mexican | dutch    |

