The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, skateboard, boat, bus
 1. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person playing bridge is between the person driving the helicopter and the owner of the lizard##2
 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is the owner of the hamster##1
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 6. the person playing poker is in an even position##4
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 8. the person playing bridge is the person drinking 7up##1
 9. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
10. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
11. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
12. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Pet    | snake    | lizard      | hamster          | chinchilla    |
| Game   | canasta | snooker       | bridge | poker |
