 8. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
 9. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
10. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person eating peas##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Cigar      | bluemaster   | dunhill   | alhambra     | pall-mall   |
| Color   | amber  | blue       | emerald | grey |
| Food           | cauliflower     | zucchini   | peas     | watermelon     |
| Transport         | ship | van | trike   | snowmobile |

