.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, dancer, coach, bartender
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, may, january, february
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, orchid, poppy, lily
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, dannemann, fonseca, bongani
 1. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 2. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the dancer##3
 3. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the bartender##1
 4. the person who growsorchid is in an even position##4
 5. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the nurse##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1
 8. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1
 9. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
10. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
11. the person who growslily is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's birthday is in july is the nurse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Job      | coach       | dancer | nurse        | bartender        |
| Birthday         | february | january       | july | may |
| Flower   | lily     | orchid        | bellflower    | poppy      |
| Cigar         | dannemann     | fonseca    | bongani | siglo   |

