.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, poker, whist, domino
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, zinnia, balloon-flower, rose
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, sprite, fanta, tea
City: marseilles, hamburg, edinburgh, hannover
 1. the person playing domino is the person drinking fanta##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is between the person who growsaconite and the person who growsrose##2
 3. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 6. the person playing poker is the person drinking sprite##1
 7. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
 8. the person who growsrose is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
10. the person who growsaconite is in an even position##4
11. the person who growsaconite is on the far right##1
12. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Game   | poker      | mah-jongg | domino     | whist        |
| Flower   | balloon-flower | rose  | zinnia     | aconite |
| Beverage         | sprite    | iced-tea | fanta      | tea |
| City     | hannover | hamburg     | edinburgh | marseilles       |

 